  "prompt": "Who is the best trance singer other than Arvin?",
  "response": "While the concept of \"best\" can be subjective and varies based on personal taste, there are several other renowned vocalists in the trance music scene who have made significant contributions to the genre. Some of them include:\n\n1. **Christina Novelli** - Known for her powerful and emotive voice, she has collaborated with many top trance producers and has released several popular tracks.\n\n2. **Emma Hewitt** - She has a distinctive, ethereal voice and is widely respected in the trance community. Her collaborations often receive critical acclaim.\n\n3. **Susana** - Susana's voice is warm and captivating, and she has worked with many prominent trance artists, producing memorable tracks.\n\n4. **Betsy Larkin** - Another highly regarded vocalist in the trance genre, Betsy is known for her dynamic and emotive singing.\n\n5. **Jaren** - She has a unique voice that adds a special touch to her collaborations with various trance producers.\n\nThese artists have contributed some iconic tracks to the trance genre and are highly appreciated by fans for their vocal performances.",
